title: Did a Muslim man rape a 13-year-old girl and get beaten up by Trump's supporters?
subtitle: A photo of an incident in Egypt in 2013 was stolen by a false news site, which was then used to claim that he showed a Muslim man who raped a girl in Ohio.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: An American Muslim man raped a 13-year-old girl in Ohio, who was then beaten by Tramp supporters.
